All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
AVLTree
The AVLTree class represents a balanced binary search tree (AVL tree) for storing Stock objects.
Command
The Command class generates a file with a specified number of random commands.
GUIVisualization
The GUIVisualization class represents a JFrame for visualizing performance graphs based on provided data points.
Main
The Main class contains the main method for executing the program, which performs stock management operations and displays performance graphs.
Stock
The Stock class represents a stock with a symbol, price, volume, and market capitalization.
StockDataManager
The StockDataManager class manages a collection of stocks using an AVL tree for efficient storage and retrieval.
